'''海外收入豁免'''是[[美国|美国]]税收制度中的一项政策。通常来说，美国对其公民或居民在全球范围的收入进行课税。然而，在海外工作的公民或居民的应纳税收入可以得到部分的豁免。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web | url = https://www.irs.gov/individuals/international-taxpayers/foreign-earned-income-exclusion | title = Foreign Earned Income Exclusion | work = IRS | accessdate = 2021-01-31 | archive-date = 2017-10-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171030101058/https://www.irs.gov/individuals/international-taxpayers/foreign-earned-income-exclusion | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/26/911 | title = 26 U.S. Code § 911 - Citizens or residents of the United States living abroad U.S. Code | work = Cornell Law School | accessdate = 2021-01-31 | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411041040/http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/26/911 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/>单个纳税人的最高海外收入豁免额度受货币[[通货膨胀|通货膨胀]]或紧缩影响，截止到2019年，该最高豁免额度为105,900美元。<ref name=revproc>{{Cite web | url = https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-drop/rp-18-57.pdf | title = Revenue procedure | work = irs | accessdate = 2021-01-31 | archive-date = 2021-03-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210318062556/https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-drop/rp-18-57.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>多人进行联合报税时，最多使用两份该额度。海外收入豁免只对美国以外的工资或自雇收入起作用。[[纳税人|纳税人]]需要在2555表格上披露有关海外收入的信息。

